{"type": "article", "id": 30227, "title": "樱桃形的厨房工具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-27T22:59:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607272235059XWZaVOyfPeu3LGi.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>以色列设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/jennye589\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jenny Pokryvailo</a> 曾经为家居用品品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计过一款尼斯湖怪造型的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/5660.html\">勺子</a>，今天要介绍的 Mon Cherry 是她的最新作品。Mon Cherry 由四颗独立的“樱桃”和一片“绿叶”构成，“樱桃”可以用作量勺，“绿叶”则是一个分蛋器。用这么一款可爱的厨具组合来制作蛋糕，心情似乎也变得更加愉快。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/kitchen/products/mon-cherry-measuring-spoons-and-egg-separator\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 16 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727223523ZGTmCnKvsYUkeDSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727223521ris57HMeuhO8CqAR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708478\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727223521ZYosevT2d7whjJIU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727223521IoDqh4K785rQJadU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.434167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}